## Overall Assessment

The `lrda_website` repository exhibits high CI/CD maturity and reflects modern DevOps practices.

Key strengths include:

- Multi-stage pipeline architecture
- Intelligent PR vs push handling
- Automated preview deployments
- Environment-aware production deployment
